snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS UNCHAINED χ – Development Team Message
snippet.description:
Kingdom Hearts Unchained χ is the first mobile game from the Kingdom Hearts franchise!

iOS: http://bit.ly/uxios
Android: http://bit.ly/uxgoo

Journey through over 200 quests in a world that brings Disney & Square Enix characters to life.
Explore Disney worlds in a charming illustration style by customizing your avatar and collecting medals of beloved characters!
Dress for adventure, or dress for fun! Defeat the Heartless for rewards on your own or defeat the raid bosses with your friends by connecting with them!

Facebook: http://bit.ly/khfb1
Instagram: http://bit.ly/khinst
Kingdom Hearts Unchained χ Twitter: http://bit.ly/khuxtw
Kingdom Hearts Twitter: http://bit.ly/khtwee
